main_body:
Regulation (EC) No 1974/2006 is amended as follows:
(1) in paragraphs (2) and (4) of Article 9, ‘1 %’ is replaced by ‘3 %’;
(2) in Article 14, the following paragraph 5 is added:
(3) in Article 21, the following paragraph 3 is added:
(4) in the second subparagraph of Article 27(12), ‘2013’ is replaced by ‘2014’;
(5) in Article 31, the following paragraph 5 is added:
(6) in Article 32, the following second paragraph is added:
(7) in Article 32a, ‘2013’ is replaced by ‘2014’;
(8) the following Article 41a is inserted:
(a) expenditure relating to the ex-ante evaluation of programmes;
(b) preparatory costs for the development of local development strategies;
(c) expenditure relating to other preparatory activities, provided that they are:
(i) directly linked to the activities of the current rural development programmes; and
(ii) necessary to ensure continuity as regards the implementation of rural development policy and a smooth passage from one programming period to the following programming period.
(9) the following Article 41b is inserted in Chapter III, Section 2:
